@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cytjtb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin((v0 / (v0 + 0.07 * v1 + 0.23)))
    v2 = (v1 + wp.abs(0.21))
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.97)) * v1)
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v1 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.89) + v1) / wp.exp((v0 + 0.07 - tmp + 0.09)))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v2 + 0.81) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.55)))
    tmp = v0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((tmp + 0.02 - tmp + 0.52)))
    data[tid] = v0
